name: Bictory
description: We are builders specializing in Blockchain Domains and Exclusive NFT marketplace across Blockchains. Our goal is to create interoperable Blockchain Domains with enhanced use cases. Our efforts involve launching a variety of domain names and providing resources to cater to the needs of Web3 projects and users. It's worth noting that our expansion isn't confined to just one domain name; we are committed to continually adding more options for all the Web3 projects. For example: .Art, .Music, .Sport, .Game, .Meta. Bictory received 2 grants from Concordium Foundation and 1 from MultiversX.
